{"article_id":"0qMTA3tg35QHJ8nu","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"President Trump clarified Sunday","depth":7},{"id":1,"text":"that he believes the assessment of U.S. intelligence agencies","depth":8},{"id":2,"text":"that Russia meddled in last year ' s presidential election ,","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"but also said","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"he believes","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"Russian President Vladimir Putin is \" sincere \" in his denials of interference .","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"\" I believe","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"that he feels","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"that he and Russia did not meddle in the election , \"","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"Mr. Trump said of Mr. Putin at a news conference in Hanoi with Vietnam ' s president .","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"\" As to whether I believe it ,","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"I ' m with our agencies .","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"As currently led by fine people ,","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"I believe very much in our intelligence agencies . \"","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"On Saturday , Mr. Trump said","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"the former heads of the FBI , the CIA and the Office of the Director of National Intelligence were \" hacks \"","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"whose judgment he questioned on the matter of Russian meddling .","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"The president ,","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"who now has new people","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"heading all three agencies ,","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"said Sunday","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"that he has worked \" very strongly \" with the new leadership in U.S. intelligence .","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"The CIA and other U.S. intelligence agencies have concluded","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"that Russia meddled in the 2016 election","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"to help Mr. Trump defeat Democrat Hillary Clinton .","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"A special counsel ' s examination of potential collusion between Moscow and Trump campaign aides so far has led to indictments against Mr. Trump ' s former campaign chairman and another top aide for crimes","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"unrelated to the campaign ,","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"and a guilty plea from a Trump foreign policy adviser .","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"Sen. John McCain , Arizona Republican , said in a statement","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"that Mr. Trump ' s belief in Mr. Putin ' s denial was \" naive . \"","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"\" There ' s nothing ' America First '","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"about taking the word of a KGB colonel over that of the American intelligence community , \"","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"Mr. McCain said .","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"\" Vladimir Putin does not have America ' s interests at heart . \"","depth":7},{"id":34,"text":"In a tweet Sunday , the president bashed the \" haters and fools \"","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"he said","depth":7},{"id":36,"text":"were questioning his efforts","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"to improve relations with Russia ,","depth":7},{"id":38,"text":"and accused critics of \" playing politics \"","depth":6},{"id":39,"text":"and hurting the U.S .","depth":6},{"id":40,"text":"Referring to his earlier comments about Mr. Putin ' s denials ,","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"Mr. Trump told reporters Sunday ,","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"\" What I said there is that","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"I believe","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"he believes that ,","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"and that ' s very important for somebody to believe .","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"What he believes is what he believes .","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"What I believe is that we have to get to work . \"","depth":6},{"id":48,"text":"He said again","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"that the U.S. needs Russia ' s help on issues","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"ranging from North Korea to Syria .","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"\" We have to get to work","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"to solve Syria ,","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"to solve North Korea ,","depth":11},{"id":54,"text":"to solve Ukraine ,","depth":12},{"id":55,"text":"to solve terrorism , \"","depth":12},{"id":56,"text":"the president said .","depth":8},{"id":57,"text":"He also pointed to recent U.S. sanctions against Moscow over the election meddling .","depth":7},{"id":58,"text":"\" People don ' t realize","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"Russia has been very , very heavily sanctioned , \"","depth":11},{"id":60,"text":"he said .","depth":11},{"id":61,"text":"\" They were sanctioned at a very high level ,","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"and that took place very recently .","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"It ' s now time","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"to get back to healing a world","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"that is shattered and broken . \"","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"Mr. Trump commented on the Russia election issue for the second straight day Sunday","depth":4},{"id":67,"text":"shortly before he arrived in the Philippines , the final stop on a five-country trip to Asia .","depth":4},{"id":68,"text":"In Manila , Mr. Trump is meeting with Philippine President Rodrigo Duterte","depth":4},{"id":69,"text":"and will attend a pair of international summits .","depth":4},{"id":70,"text":"⦁ This article is based in part on wire service reports .","depth":1}],"relations":[{"parent":141,"left":140,"right":70,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":140,"left":136,"right":139,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":136,"left":104,"right":135,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":104,"left":84,"right":103,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":84,"left":76,"right":83,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":76,"left":73,"right":75,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":73,"left":0,"right":72,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":72,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":75,"left":3,"right":74,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"p